Project 0  - Identity Incident Investigator "Version 1.0" : 
My goal is not to fix the issue automatically.
My goal is to help the engineer investigate faster and with more confidence.

Product Vision: 
AI-IAM Identity Incident Investigator is an AI-powered investigation assistant that helps Microsoft Identity engineers diagnose authentication and authorization issues 
by correlating Microsoft Graph data, audit logs, Conditional Access policies, and sign-in events into a single evidence-based report.


